*[[7 March]] – [[Matthew Fisher (musician)|Matthew Fisher]] ([[Procol Harum]])
*[[21 March]] – [[Ray Dorset]] ([[Mungo Jerry]])
*[[1 April]] – [[Ronnie Lane]], singer, songwriter and guitarist ([[The Faces]]) (died [[1997 in British music|1997]])
